race.comment: BAR ROOM ROSES (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her slick win the start prior, getting around this track over 375m in 21.91. Has the ability and expected to go close again. CROATIAN COMET (5) was the fastest winner on the program last time out, running away to score by 3 lengths (21.79) at this track. Deserved serious consideration again. QWERTY (6) has been in the money at 15 of 37 starts, winning two back before another minor placings latest when third (22.54) over 375m at this track. Expected to feature on best form. GRACIOUS GIFT (3) has strong credentials over this journey.
